	(257,1,'2015-04-15 16:45:06','2015-04-15 16:45:06','Exterior Color\r\nJade Green \r\n\r\nInterior Seating\r\n18 Passengers \r\n\r\nSleeping Accommodations\r\n12 Private bunks \r\n\r\nFeatures\r\n\r\nLuxurious front and rear lounges each separately and independently furnished with Hunter Green perimeter leather seating, granite ice coolers, large TV\'s, premium surround sound stereo systems w/ DVD/VHS/CD/FM and subwoofers.  Each lounge has independent In-Motion DIRECTV.\r\n\r\nThe fore lounge has kitchenette with refrigerator/freezer, microwave, coffee maker, and stainless steel sink w/ hot/cold water and dinette table.  It also is equipped with restroom with full service sinks, vanity mirrors and accent lighting.\r\n\r\nEach lounge has dark tinted windows with both semi and full privacy window shades.  Both lounges have accent lighted mirrored ceilings and various mood lighting.\r\n\r\nBetween both lounges you will find the sleeping area separated by two privacy doors.\r\n\r\nThere are 12 private sleeping bunks.  Each bunk has independent AC/Heat, personal lighting, A/C outlets and privacy curtains.\r\n\r\nAdditionally, this Coach has (2) large storage bays underneath to hold vast amounts of luggage or gear.  The generator can supply power for all the coaches\' amenities for 3 full days in a stationary position and also is equipped with shore power for extended stays.\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\nAdditional Options\r\n\r\nClassic Thunder Limousine can also provide the following: \r\n\r\nEnclosed trailers\r\n\r\n45ft. Telescoping Flag Pole w/banner poles for promotions/advertising\r\n\r\nOutside tail gating flat screen TV with custom 6ft. stand and DIRECTV\r\n\r\nStainless Steel LP grill\r\n\r\nLarge premium outdoor stereo system\r\n','Executive Tour Bus','','publish','closed','closed','','executive-tour-bus','','','2015-04-18 17:16:22','2015-04-18 17:16:22','',0,'http://local.classicthunderlimos/?post_type=vehicles&#038;p=257',0,'vehicles','',0),
